  "detailed_description": "The Legend of HyperStar is a roguelike,Darksoul like indiegame.<br><br>Game features<br>Play a well-trained, beautiful and powerful brave girl, challenge various levels. Through the fantastic forest, the secret place.<br>Every time I fail to challenge, I will accumulate wealth and experience to improve myself in my reincarnation.<br>Get more powerful props, strengthen runes and skills, and get better weapons and equipment in random events. Finally defeat all kinds of enemies. Challenge the powerful devil.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/c0e61ae9b2dc78a93850a7f2d63d87bb.poster.avif?t=1598978527\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/c0e61ae9b2dc78a93850a7f2d63d87bb.webm?t=1598978527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/c0e61ae9b2dc78a93850a7f2d63d87bb.mp4?t=1598978527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/88c3d244d2458e25faae774d5eee55fb.poster.avif?t=1598978527\" width=400 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/88c3d244d2458e25faae774d5eee55fb.webm?t=1598978527\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/88c3d244d2458e25faae774d5eee55fb.mp4?t=1598978527\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1308560/extras/272fa73b9fdf6efac43b60e6bf2